() Tj T*
(REVISION SUMMARY) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(This version updates the original requirements document to match the implemented) Tj T*
(application now present in the repository.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Added) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Audited inventory adjustment workflow, including manual corrections, "deplete) Tj T*
(    remaining", and restoration of depleted lots.) Tj T*
(  - Explicit account reset CLI and local reset workflow.) Tj T*
(  - UUID public/user-facing identifiers for recipes and batches.) Tj T*
(  - Friendly two-word batch slugs retained separately from batch identifiers.) Tj T*
(  - Suggested two-word recipe titles.) Tj T*
(  - Container cartridge capacity and capacity enforcement.) Tj T*
(  - Derived batch storage and depletion states driven by container assignment and container) Tj T*
(    use.) Tj T*
(  - Tracking of batch quantity cleared from emptied containers.) Tj T*
(  - Settings page backup workflow.) Tj T*
(  - Tenant-scoped JSON and CSV exports.) Tj T*
(  - Selenium browser workflow tests, including a complete .357 Magnum workflow.) Tj T*
(  - Docker Selenium profile for opt-in end-to-end browser testing.) Tj T*
(  - Help/context download endpoint for LLM-oriented app context.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Removed or Deferred) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Recipe component alternatives are no longer supported in the implemented workflow. Each) Tj T*
(    core recipe role may have only one exact item. To use a different primer, case, bullet,) Tj T*
(    or powder, the user creates a separate recipe.) Tj T*
(  - Recipe two-word slugs were replaced by UUID identifiers. Two-word generation is now) Tj T*
(    used for suggested recipe titles, not recipe IDs.) Tj T*
(  - Direct binary upload of source materials is not implemented. Source records can store) Tj T*
(    citation, URL, page, file name metadata, and notes.) Tj T*
(  - Return-to-new-lot behavior is not implemented as part of the return endpoint. Returned) Tj T*
(    inventory can be credited to the source lot or to an existing compatible lot; a new lot) Tj T*
(    can be created separately through the inventory workflow.) Tj T*
(  - Google OAuth, email-based password recovery, nested containers, full container) Tj T*
(    occupancy history, Garmin file import, and load-data recommendation remain future) Tj T*
(    candidates.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Modified) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Batch lifecycle now separates production completion from storage assignment. A batch) Tj T*
(    moves from `UNDER PRODUCTION` to `PRODUCED`; storage-related states are derived from) Tj T*
(    container assignments.) Tj T*
(  - Batch depletion state names now use `PARTIALLY DEPLETED` and `DEPLETED` instead of) Tj T*
(    `PARTIALLY USED` and `USED`.) Tj T*
(  - `PARTIALLY USED` and `USED` are container states, not batch states.) Tj T*
(  - Container `RETIRED` is not implemented in the current state machine.) Tj T*
(  - Inventory lot `opened_on` is system-managed and set when an active lot first has) Tj T*
(    drawdown, not accepted from lot creation input.) Tj T*
(Page 1 of 27) Tj
