(  - Existing active sessions for that user are revoked.) Tj T*
(  - Login returns a `password_reset_required` response.) Tj T*
(  - The rendering app directs the user to `/reset-password`.) Tj T*
(  - The user enters email and a new password.) Tj T*
(  - Reset is accepted only if `LOCAL_RESET_ENABLED=true` and the account is marked) Tj T*
(    `reset_required`.) Tj T*
