(7.7 Inventory Adjustments) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The application supports audited inventory adjustments for an inventory lot.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(An adjustment records:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Owning user.) Tj T*
(  - Inventory lot.) Tj T*
(  - Created timestamp.) Tj T*
(  - Quantity change.) Tj T*
(  - Unit.) Tj T*
(  - Available quantity before.) Tj T*
