(  - Notes.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Rules:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - Adjustment quantity must be non-zero.) Tj T*
(  - Count-based adjustments must be whole numbers.) Tj T*
(  - Adjustment cannot reduce available quantity below zero.) Tj T*
(  - Adjustment is blocked while the lot has active reservations.) Tj T*
(  - The user can request `deplete_remaining`, which creates an adjustment equal to negative) Tj T*
(    available quantity.) Tj T*
(  - If the adjustment depletes the lot, the lot is marked depleted and inactive.) Tj T*
(  - A positive later adjustment can restore availability and clear depleted state, but it) Tj T*
(    does not automatically reactivate the lot.) Tj T*
