(8.3 Recipe Lifecycle) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Recipe states are:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - `UNDER DEVELOPMENT`.) Tj T*
(  - `UNDER TEST`.) Tj T*
(  - `APPROVED`.) Tj T*
(  - `RETIRED`.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Allowed transitions are:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  - `UNDER DEVELOPMENT` -> `UNDER TEST`.) Tj T*
(  - `UNDER TEST` -> `UNDER DEVELOPMENT`.) Tj T*
(  - `UNDER TEST` -> `APPROVED`.) Tj T*
